	<h1 class="title">同程和韩国乐天成立合资公司，瞄准韩国旅游市场</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/130051/small/130051.jpg?1435571000" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">温欣语 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-11 14:41:12 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18920/medium/18920.jpg?1449815057" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


